name: Stinky Fish
description:
Entry for the TriJam 178 

My entry for the jam . 

You need to get the key by getting the blue player to it to open the door and go the next level . 

Press R to reload if stuck

For this entry i tried to many stuff , but i did more than i can handle for three hours of work .
There is alos the level design that still undone  etc . 
But it was a cool theme  to jam to .
